{"tid":1913283,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"Fight for freedom(賣鞋)食人血饅頭 連手足錢都要賺","createTime":"2020-03-06T15:56:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T22:46:28.000Z","uid":68211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b724cff1359881bf72cd8e949117290725c0931a","tid":1913283,"uid":68211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:56:43.000Z","msg":"Fight for freedom(Facebook) 賣假converse鞋，又扮送鞋比手足，點知連手足錢都賺盡。手足叫我提醒大家唔好中伏，希望大家唔好幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R5GxYxb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR5GxYxb.jpg&h=15236394&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我搵左幾位苦主，其中一位更係手足。手足因經濟困難想退錢，但店主多次拒絕，死都要賺手足錢。<br />\n<br />\n條仆街吹到會送鞋比手足，但當手足真係有需要時，就話自己冇生意，唔肯退款，但明明好多人落order。（另外送貨地址係手足朋友既租住地址，唔洗擔心店主會公開手足住址<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n以下係手足朋友同店主既對話圖 :<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dDsUstc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdDsUstc.png&h=740e6eb1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2SWqy8d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2SWqy8d.png&h=6a803b09&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q0d4PGz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ0d4PGz.png&h=18ce7135&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tj1qy8f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTj1qy8f.jpg&h=66a4deda&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z46YT8g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ46YT8g.png&h=1d00b766&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LbJAbUW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLbJAbUW.jpg&h=2ffb0e04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另一位苦主比左錢仲收唔到貨，詳情： <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/271044893806518/permalink/343911933186480/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F271044893806518%2Fpermalink%2F343911933186480%2F&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnIc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=7c622a3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/271044893806518/permalink/343911933186480/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n假鞋實物：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x2O07ve.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx2O07ve.jpg&h=10adaf93&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kK9Lzaf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkK9Lzaf.jpg&h=253a8023&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8rwRuJB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8rwRuJB.jpg&h=57fd29de&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8MsQLgX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8MsQLgX.jpg&h=e733ad5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他人都收到假鞋：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ewP35hz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FewP35hz.jpg&h=4345bfc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有人對鞋踭係假tag（淘寶貨）：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i11ugpk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi11ugpk.jpg&h=e33a14f0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E7jGRXF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE7jGRXF.jpg&h=4c213047&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n店主話自己會送鞋比手足，先唔講佢咁撚樣公開哂人地啲facebook名...比我搵到個ac係得3個friend，唔知係咪店主自己開分身ac呢。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/03/06/234752_b1ebcc68cdc39b572fccc25d8b55e2e0.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F03%2F06%2F234752_b1ebcc68cdc39b572fccc25d8b55e2e0.jpeg&h=4e9e867b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UrnUsxj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUrnUsxj.jpg&h=f31af5b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有其他，不過費事慢慢搵啲ac<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PX7dH53.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPX7dH53.jpg&h=4309373f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外佢有個carousell account：<a href=\"https://hk.carousell.com/sniper_fung\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.carousell.com%2Fsniper_fung&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnIc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=83fc26d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.carousell.com/sniper_fung</a><br />\n<br />\n地址 :柴灣泗興隆工業大廈11樓<br />\nWechat : Sniperfung1986<br />\nWhatapps : 65030048<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好再中伏！另外手足經濟方面暫時解決左，大家唔洗擔心。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf30124111c905cfd2eeb18708dbcb33f8f3b7ff","tid":1913283,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T16:10:39.000Z","msg":"Lm<br />\n<br />\n利申從來唔buy呢啲打卡饅頭"},{"pid":"1a9f02459bc45c7a339cf42e7a39aa8e52f90778","tid":1913283,"uid":198523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T22:46:28.000Z","msg":"push"}]}